   <body>
      <p>Press the <uicontrol> Section </uicontrol> button to show detailed information about the
         measurement data of a section. You can quickly change to another section by pressing the
         Section arrow buttons.</p>
      <p>Press on a bottle image to show only that bottle and related information. Press again on
         the bottle image to show all bottles again. Press on a bottle to see more data about a
         specific cavity.<fig id="fig_rxp_5rn_fcc">
            <image href="media/image1.jpg"
                   placement="break"
                   id="image_sxp_5rn_fcc"
                   align="center"/>
         </fig>
      </p>
      <p>Press on a graph to zoom on the image. Press again on the graph to return to the normal
            view.<fig id="fig_hxn_1sn_fcc">
            <image href="media/image2.jpg"
                   placement="break"
                   align="center"
                   id="image_ixn_1sn_fcc"/>
         </fig>
      </p>
      <p>Press on the up and down arrow keys to change the Region. Press on the<uicontrol> arrow
            keys</uicontrol> &lt; &gt; to go back and forward in time.</p>
      <p>Press the Squares Icon to expand the view and show the bottles above each other.<fig id="fig_xg1_bsn_fcc">
            <image href="media/image3.jpg"
                   placement="break"
                   id="image_yg1_bsn_fcc"
                   align="center"/>
         </fig>
      </p>
      <p>Press the <uicontrol>Filter Icon</uicontrol> to filter the graph data. The screens below
         show no filter (left) and one filter (right).<fig id="fig_zcp_2sn_fcc">
            <image href="media/image4.jpg"
                   placement="break"
                   id="image_adp_2sn_fcc"
                   align="center"/>
         </fig>
         <fig id="fig_wyn_fsn_fcc">
            <image href="media/image5.jpg"
                   placement="break"
                   id="image_xyn_fsn_fcc"
                   align="center"/>
         </fig>
         <fig id="fig_qcc_hsn_fcc">
            <image href="media/image6.jpg"
                   placement="break"
                   id="image_rcc_hsn_fcc"
                   align="center"/>
         </fig>
      </p>
